Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.20,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Kakyoin? {start copy paste from 45}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.62,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.79,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I know how to reveal the secret of Dio's Stand! {end copy paste from 45}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.16,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:46.77,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,As Kakyoin Noriaki gazed at Hierophant Green, \Nhe began to recall memories of his youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:53.86,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,Your son, Noriaki, doesn't seem to be making any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:58.53,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nobody dislikes him, but he refuses to open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.95,Flashback,Teacher,0,0,0,,I'm worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.92,Flashback,Mama Kak,0,0,0,,I'm his mother, and even I don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.59,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,When I was younger, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.05,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,"If you live in a city where you're bound to meet a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.97,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,...and you spend your entire life there, will you ever truly get to know those people, and will they know you just as well in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:27.10,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,The address books of my classmates\N are filled with the names of their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.40,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,They must have at least fifty friends each.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.73,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Maybe even a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.11,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,My mother has my father, and my father has my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:36.32,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,...but I have nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.24,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,The rock stars on TV must have tens of thousands of friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.70,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,...but I have nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:46.75,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I'll probably never meet anyone who sees me for who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:52.42,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,All because not a single friend of mine can see my Hierophant Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:56.63,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Anyone who can't see it will never truly understand me."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:04.27,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar, Jotaro, Polnareff, and Abdul \Nmade me realize what true friends are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:10.94,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,When I remember that Abdul and Iggy are gone,\N it gives me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:15.44,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because they were\N the first friends I shared a common goal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.78,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,This journey to defeat Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:23.20,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,In these short few weeks, we've become close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:29.00,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kakyoin Noriaki gazed at Hierophant Green and thought to himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.17,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,"I'll make it invisible to everyone, just like it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:39.01,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Yes, to reveal Dio's true identity and finally defeat him, \NI'll make its presence completely disappear!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:14.94,Title 3,title,0,0,0,,{\fad(985,689)\pos(88,593.333)}Episode 46: Dio's World Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.19,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.57,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That car got totaled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.15,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.15,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gramps and Dio are on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.24,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Only Kakyoin and Joseph are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.46,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I see. They're attempting a pincer attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.55,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jotaro and Polnareff must be preparing to attack from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.55,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,A useless effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...Kakyoin's Hierophant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.32,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Hierophant's barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.51,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.17,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:31.56,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Using the barrier my Hierophant created,\N I can hit you within twenty meters from any direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:36.23,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I can also sense every move you or The World make!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:55.62,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Take this, Dio! Twenty-meter radius Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.17,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You fool! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:06.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World's true power, as its name suggests, is to reign supreme over the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.14,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Show me your Stand, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.26,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.52,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.52,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He went flying away instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.03,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.49,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:34.12,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,W-What... just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.04,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.38,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It's over... I won't survive this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.68,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I can't speak... or even lift a finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.97,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It's 5:15...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.73,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,That means it's about midnight in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.27,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I wonder what my parents are doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.44,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Maybe they went to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.44,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I hope they aren't worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:16.74,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kakyoin Noriaki's final thoughts were not of his parents in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:25.38,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Though he cared deeply for his parents, when his mind drifted to the final unsolved puzzle, his thoughts of them were put aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:31.05,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I can sense every movement made in my Hierophant's barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:36.39,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,But somehow Dio ripped the barrier apart all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.39,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Why didn't it rip strand-by-strand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:44.40,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,They broke simultaneously; not a millisecond between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:49.15,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,How did he destroy a twenty-meter large barrier all at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.15,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.41,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Without even a moment passing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.25,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,How... All at once...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.87,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.87,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I-I can't stand around and do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.13,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hermit{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.01,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Joseph, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:22.69,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Isn't it fitting that Joestar blood is the only way for\N Jonathan's perfect body to become completely mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.48,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:29.48,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,How could he destroy them all at once without any time passing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.99,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Time passing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.74,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.32,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.24,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,The clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.04,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I-I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:50.38,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,H-How is that possible? There's no other explanation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.01,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I-I need to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.89,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Somehow I need to tell them this terrifying truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.97,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Somehow I have to tell Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.64,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,If I don't, all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.11,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,...will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.78,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,How dare you hurt Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:15.15,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm taking that body back for my Granny Erina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:20.03,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Erina? Ah, you mean that simpleton country girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.16,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Such foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.41,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I will drink your blood to commemorate your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.90,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Joseph Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.10,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:13.67,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,M-My final Emerald... Splash...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What's this? He completely missed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:24.43,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,He must have seen it fit to go out with a bang using what little strength he had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.85,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.81,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin wouldn't do something pointless at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.94,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Why did he shoot there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.03,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,What could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.57,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Was he trying to tell me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:41.53,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It's... a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.49,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It's all I could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.33,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:52.00,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Please get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:57.30,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Please... figure it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.39,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.06,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kakyoin Noriaki has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.07,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hermit Purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.40,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.32,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The energy of the sun, the Ripple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:24.33,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You senile old fool! Your Stand is too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.45,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You cannot escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.88,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin, why did you shoot the clock tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:43.89,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,What were you trying to tell me by shooting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.85,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,It must have been important!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.23,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I-It's Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.31,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Dio is chasing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.77,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,But where's Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.86,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin, you couldn't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:04.11,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Did you actually discover the secret of Dio's Stand from that brief encounter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.74,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,He destroyed the clock with an Emerald Splash...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.29,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,...which destroyed the clock hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.92,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,...and stopped the clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.63,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,N-No way! Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.55,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The secret of Dio's The World...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.10,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...is that it can stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:34.73,Flashback,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Take this, Dio! Twenty-meter radius Emerald Splash! {Same as line 50}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.86,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.97,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,Behold, The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:14.64,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,While time is stopped,\N you will neither see nor feel anything that befalls you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.69,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,Die, Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.58,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,You don't even realize I have killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.58,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,You will never know what truly transpired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.96,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I-I get it, Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.84,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You sent me your dying message...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.72,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...and I read it loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.19,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It stops time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.20,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,His Stand lets him move while time is stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.70,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He's dangerous! {\i1}Really{\i0} dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.79,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Calm down! Calm down and think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.71,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,The word "panic" isn't in my vocabulary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.54,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,I need to think of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.05,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,I need to find a way to overcome and defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.13,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,H-He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.98,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,W-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Can't hit me, Dio?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.69,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to drink my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:47.44,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You've guarded yourself by channeling the Ripple around your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:54.20,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,When your Hermit Purple is imbued with the Ripple, \Nit acts as a high-voltage wire wrapped around your body, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.58,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You're quite the schemer, you cunning old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.71,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I could say the same of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:09.59,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You realized I was using the Ripple \Nand made sure not to touch me, you shrewd bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:14.18,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But I think I finally figured out how your Stand works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:20.27,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Dio, even though you can stop time,\N it doesn't work for very long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:23.44,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Only about three or four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:34.58,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Any longer, and you would have just killed us back at the mansion,\N saving yourself the trouble of chasing us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:39.29,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So you already know how The World works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.33,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.38,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin was the one who figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.21,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I refuse to let his death go in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.22,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,How will you use this information against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:57.81,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Just what can your pathetic Ripple do against{\i1} me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.98,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hermit Purple and the Ripple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:02.85,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.02,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I needn't touch your Ripple to attack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.20,Main,Dipshits,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.91,Main,Dipshits,0,0,0,,Some old fart fell outta the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.12,Main,Dipshits,0,0,0,,He's just like Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.96,Main,Dipshits,0,0,0,,The fuck were ya doin' on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.04,Main,Dipshits,0,0,0,,Prowlin' fer some nice ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.55,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.30,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,J-Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.14,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.31,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.35,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jotaro! What perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:48.07,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But he's still not quite within my range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Joseph must be taken care of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:57.45,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Jotaro! The secret of his Stand, The World, is time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.58,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,His Stand can stop ti{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.33,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:18.85,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,At first, I could only stop time for a mere blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:27.10,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,However, as the wound on my neck began to heal,\N I could stop time for two seconds, then eventually three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Now I am at five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:38.87,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Although it is strange to consider it five seconds\N since time has stopped, it is indeed five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.79,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Eventually I will reach a minute, then ten minutes, and then an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Then as long as I wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:56.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It's quite thrilling.\N Soon I will be able to stop time for even longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Careful now, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.43,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I see you're still guarding yourself with the Ripple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:08.35,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Your troublesome Ripple may have been a nuisance to me \None hundred years ago, but now it is powerless before The World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Joseph, grandson of Jonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.33,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...this is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.17,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,One more second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.88,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:57.99,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.49,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,S-Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.12,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,R-Run away... J-Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.58,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,D-Don't... get near him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.38,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,K-Keep your...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.34,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...d-distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.26,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Stay away... Stay away from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:27.10,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Y-You're no... match...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:37.07,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Kakyoin has also been dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:41.24,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,And I suppose Polnareff is hiding nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But it matters not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.20,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Now, Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.21,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.21,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You asshole...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.05,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.93,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Oh? You've decided to approach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:05.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You wish to face the mighty Dio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:09.18,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Despite your grandfather, Joseph,\N discovering the secret of The World...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:17.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...he was nothing more than a desperate, pathetic old man; no better than a student rushing to complete their exam before time has run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:21.45,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,The thing is, I gotta get closer to beat the living shit out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.03,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Then come as close as you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.17,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:41.59,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Much too slow! The World is the ultimate Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:47.35,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Even if you wish to ignore its ability to stop time, its speed and power far exceed Star Platinum's!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.27,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,So it's the same kind of Stand as Star Platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:55.15,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Powerful and precise, but short-ranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:21:02.19,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I wanted to find out how powerful The World is compared to your inferior Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.36,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...however, that no longer appears necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:10.20,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Find out what? You barely grazed my leg. Didn't feel a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.91,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Though I guess you hurt my wallet by ruining my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.67,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Why can't you Joestars ever concede defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:23.34,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I suppose I shall humor you to see what more you are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora! {no reason to have 2 of this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.73,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.86,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Shall we see whose attack rush is faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:48.07,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:48.07,Secondary,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora! {Not sure if this is staying here and grey like it is, or going to the top of the screen and white}
