Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.85,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...in an instant, it appeared as though\N everything had stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:38.60,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I shall finish you here and now\N with the mighty power of The World!
