Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.97,SC Opening 2 Jap,,0,0,0,,Chikazuitekuru kessen no toki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:27.01,SC Opening 2 Jap,,0,0,0,,Utsubeki period wa Star Platinum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:33.31,SC Opening 2 Jap,,0,0,0,,Hajimattashimatta monogatari ni ubawareta mama no toki ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:39.86,SC Opening 2 Jap,,0,0,0,,Ima owari wo tsugeru tame arukitsuzukeru Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:47.70,SC Opening 2 Jap,,0,0,0,,Kuuhaku no last page ni sono kobushi wo tatakikome
