Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.35,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,635.333)}Seeking out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.47,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the slumbering legend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.31,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Scorching below us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.56,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the shifting sands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:54.11,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Our destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:54.11,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...is awoken once again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:02.74,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,The tenacious blood that burns the silent flame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.83,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,The manifestations of the Gods that have been called forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:11.29,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...we will fearlessly pierce with our swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:15.84,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,As we march towards an uncertain destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.97,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the final battle draws nearer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:27.01,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,And the one to end it all will be Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:33.31,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Our tale has begun and our time runs short
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:39.86,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,To end it all the Crusaders must continue onwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:47.70,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Let loose your fists on this blank last page!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.50,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,End of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.13,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...and the memories of your bloodline!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:04:00.05,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.26,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Ora!
